{"tid":2208014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"之前幾個港人係船到比人屈藏毒單野點?","createTime":"2020-09-18T14:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T15:01:34.000Z","uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5973e79608057cc4d83763d6f1c5ac1ae002a6f3","tid":2208014,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"好似係東南亞國家<br />\n唔係真係坐一世?"},{"pid":"dfa9857791e85b4d16d8cf121b9e6ed93db74b1a","tid":2208014,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:25:48.000Z","msg":"鄧龍威菲律賓上訴被拒　哥哥：望特區政府幫助<br />\n<br />\n#港聞 港人鄧龍威早年被菲律賓當局指控在當地藏毒，判囚終身。協助他的立法會議員謝偉俊收到消息，菲律賓的最高法院，終極駁回其上訴，他指案件存在疑點。鄧龍威哥哥希望，特區政府能夠從其他途徑協助。 (9/18/22:14) 全文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406084&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=c9eb6b2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406084&h=4322d22e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406084</a>"},{"pid":"cc317a22575692c3bc17a73e94dad8d199a63893","tid":2208014,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b050f54e156e8484ed0540fabdb88f0feff32492","tid":2208014,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc317a22575692c3bc17a73e94dad8d199a63893","tid":2208014,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"唔似 <br />\n係船上 仲有幾個港人"},{"pid":"b53d6267ac1b776bc6e2d729f3fef9dfe3c52b15","tid":2208014,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b050f54e156e8484ed0540fabdb88f0feff32492","tid":2208014,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc317a22575692c3bc17a73e94dad8d199a63893","tid":2208014,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"唔似 <br />\n係船上 仲有幾個港人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"2016年7月，香港四名長洲漁民到達菲律賓，被安排駕駛一隻漁船回中國大陸，但四人一登上船，就被警員拘捕，指控他們製毒罪。協助四名長洲漁民的立法會議員涂謹申說：「第一輪搜查是在一大堆電視台和記者面前搜船，任何東西也搜不到，當時有電視台以為告一段落，突然間在視線範圍以外，在一間房間，警方突然間話搜到毒品，當時是在沒有獨立第三者面前搜到。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ea1b528f98c77d659e15ea36c422b27a49f366","tid":2208014,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53d6267ac1b776bc6e2d729f3fef9dfe3c52b15","tid":2208014,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b050f54e156e8484ed0540fabdb88f0feff32492","tid":2208014,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc317a22575692c3bc17a73e94dad8d199a63893","tid":2208014,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"唔似 <br />\n係船上 仲有幾個港人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"2016年7月，香港四名長洲漁民到達菲律賓，被安排駕駛一隻漁船回中國大陸，但四人一登上船，就被警員拘捕，指控他們製毒罪。協助四名長洲漁民的立法會議員涂謹申說：「第一輪搜查是在一大堆電視台和記者面前搜船，任何東西也搜不到，當時有電視台以為告一段落，突然間在視線範圍以外，在一間房間，警方突然間話搜到毒品，當時是在沒有獨立第三者面前搜到。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"ys 唔知有無新消息"},{"pid":"25a2aff31b22b15384b163782e1f9251f8267165","tid":22